<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Şifre Sıfırlama Talebi</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f8f8; 
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 90%;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .content h1 {
            color: #e67e22; /* Turuncu renk */
            font-size: 28px;
        }
        .content p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
      .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #e67e22; /* Turuncu renk */
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            width: auto;
            max-width: 200px;
            text-align: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
            -webkit-appearance: none;  /* Fix for email clients */
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #d57e15;  /* Darker orange on hover */
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: #777;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .footer p {
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .emoji {
            font-size: 24px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
          
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Şifrenizi Sıfırlayın 🔑</h1>
            <p>
                Merhaba <strong>{{ user.FirstName }}</strong> 😊,<br>
                Şifrenizi sıfırlamak için aşağıdaki bağlantıya tıklayın:<br>
              <a href="{{ user.ResetLink }}" style="color: #007bff; text-decoration: none;">
        Şifreyi Sıfırla
   ✨</a>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Bu talebi siz göndermediyseniz, lütfen bu e-postayı dikkate almayın 🚫.</p>
            <p><strong>İlmek Ekibi 💖</strong></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
